Interface Regional

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SpecimenWithinDistanceOfPoint, SpecimenWithinLatitudeBounds

    public interface Regional
    Create an interface with a method that will take a container of specimens and return a container that only includes the subset of the specimens that were found within some specific region.
